description: Newly renovated Westside townhouse Single-Family conveniently located near the Broadway shops and restaurants and minutes from the T stations and the SB Seaport. This property has 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths over three levels and has been tastefully renovated this past Fall. This is a potential investment property (Est. rent - $7,500) or is a perfect Condo alternative for a growing family. The unfinished basement has the potential for additional living space or a recreational room for the kids.
